{"id":"guide/property-binding","title":"Property binding","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/property-binding.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"property-binding\" translation-result=\"on\">屬性繫結<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/property-binding#property-binding\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Property binding<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/property-binding#property-binding\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">Angular 中的屬性繫結可幫助你設定 HTML 元素或指令的屬性值。使用屬性繫結，可以執行諸如切換按鈕、以程式設計方式設定路徑，以及在元件之間共享值之類別的功能。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Property binding in Angular helps you set values for properties of HTML elements or directives. Use property binding to do things such as toggle button features, set paths programmatically, and share values between components.</p>\n\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\">包含本指南中的程式碼片段的工作範例，請參閱<live-example></live-example>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">See the <live-example></live-example> for a working example containing the code snippets in this guide.</p>\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" translation-result=\"on\">前提條件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/property-binding#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Prerequisites<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/property-binding#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/architecture-components\">元件基礎</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/architecture-components\">Basics of components</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\">範本基礎</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\">Basics of templates</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/binding-syntax\">繫結語法</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/binding-syntax\">Binding syntax</a></p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"understanding-the-flow-of-data\" translation-result=\"on\">瞭解資料流<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/property-binding#understanding-the-flow-of-data\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Understanding the flow of data<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/property-binding#understanding-the-flow-of-data\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">屬性繫結在單一方向上將值從元件的屬性送到目標元素的屬性。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Property binding moves a value in one direction, from a component's property into a target element property.</p>\n\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\">有關偵聽事件的更多資訊，請參閱<a href=\"guide/event-binding\">事件繫結</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">For more information on listening for events, see <a href=\"guide/event-binding\">Event binding</a>.</p>\n\n</div>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要讀取目標元素的屬性或呼叫其方法，請參閱 <a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\">ViewChild</a> 和 <a href=\"api/core/ContentChild\">ContentChild</a> 的 API 參考手冊。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To read a target element property or call one of its methods, see the API reference for <a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\">ViewChild</a> and <a href=\"api/core/ContentChild\">ContentChild</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"binding-to-a-property\" translation-result=\"on\">繫結到屬性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/property-binding#binding-to-a-property\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Binding to a property<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/property-binding#binding-to-a-property\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要繫結到元素的屬性，請將其放在方括號 <code>[]</code> 中，這會將此屬性標識為目標屬性。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To bind to an element's property, enclose it in square brackets, <code>[]</code>, which identifies the property as a target property.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要繫結到元素的屬性，請將其括在方括號 <code>[]</code> 內，這會將此屬性標為目標屬性。目標屬性就是你要對其進行賦值的 DOM 屬性。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A target property is the DOM property to which you want to assign a value.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要為 image 元素的目標屬性（<code>src</code>）賦值，請鍵入以下程式碼：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To assign a value to a target property for the image element's <code>src</code> property, type the following code:</p>\n\n<code-example path=\"property-binding/src/app/app.component.html\" region=\"property-binding\" header=\"src/app/app.component.html\">\n&lt;<a href=\"api/common/NgOptimizedImage\" class=\"code-anchor\">img</a> alt=\"item\" [src]=\"itemImageUrl\"&gt;\n\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在大多數情況下，目標名稱是 Property（屬性）名稱，即使它看起來是 Attribute（屬性）名稱。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">In most cases, the target name is the name of a property, even when it appears to be the name of an attribute.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在這個例子中，<code>src</code> 就是 <code>&lt;<a href=\"api/common/NgOptimizedImage\" class=\"code-anchor\">img</a>&gt;</code> 元素的 Property 名稱。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">In this example, <code>src</code> is the name of the <code>&lt;<a href=\"api/common/NgOptimizedImage\" class=\"code-anchor\">img</a>&gt;</code> element property.</p>\n\n<!-- vale Angular.Google_WordListSuggestions = NO -->\n<p translation-result=\"on\">方括號 <code>[]</code> 使 Angular 將等號的右側看作動態表示式進行求值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The brackets, <code>[]</code>, cause Angular to evaluate the right-hand side of the assignment as a dynamic expression.</p>\n\n<!-- vale Angular.Google_WordListSuggestions = NO -->\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果不使用方括號，Angular 就會將右側視為字串字面量並將此屬性設定為該靜態值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Without the brackets, Angular treats the right-hand side as a string literal and sets the property to that static value.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要將字串賦值給屬性，請鍵入以下程式碼：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To assign a string to a property, type the following code:</p>\n\n<code-example path=\"property-binding/src/app/app.component.html\" region=\"no-evaluation\" header=\"src/app.component.html\">\n&lt;app-item-detail childItem=\"parentItem\"&gt;&lt;/app-item-detail&gt;\n\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">省略方括號就會渲染出字串 <code>parentItem</code>，而不是 <code>parentItem</code> 的值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Omitting the brackets renders the string <code>parentItem</code>, not the value of <code>parentItem</code>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"setting-an-element-property-to-a-component-property-value\" translation-result=\"on\">將元素的屬性設定為元件屬性的值<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/property-binding#setting-an-element-property-to-a-component-property-value\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Setting an element property to a component property value<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/property-binding#setting-an-element-property-to-a-component-property-value\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要將 <code>&lt;<a href=\"api/common/NgOptimizedImage\" class=\"code-anchor\">img</a>&gt;</code> 的 <code>src</code> 屬性繫結到元件的屬性，請將 <code>src</code> 放在方括號中，後跟等號，然後是元件的屬性。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To bind the <code>src</code> property of an <code>&lt;<a href=\"api/common/NgOptimizedImage\" class=\"code-anchor\">img</a>&gt;</code> element to a component's property, place <code>src</code> in square brackets followed by an equal sign and then the property.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用屬性 <code>itemImageUrl</code>，鍵入以下程式碼：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Using the property <code>itemImageUrl</code>, type the following code:</p>\n\n<code-example path=\"property-binding/src/app/app.component.html\" region=\"property-binding\" header=\"src/app/app.component.html\">\n&lt;<a href=\"api/common/NgOptimizedImage\" class=\"code-anchor\">img</a> alt=\"item\" [src]=\"itemImageUrl\"&gt;\n\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在元件類 <code>AppComponent</code> 中宣告 <code>itemImageUrl</code> 屬性。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Declare the <code>itemImageUrl</code> property in the class, in this case <code>AppComponent</code>.</p>\n\n<code-example path=\"property-binding/src/app/app.component.ts\" region=\"item-image\" header=\"src/app/app.component.ts\">\nitemImageUrl = '../assets/phone.svg';\n\n</code-example>\n<a id=\"colspan\"></a>\n<h4 id=\"colspan-and-colspan\" translation-result=\"on\"><code>colspan</code> 和 <code>colSpan</code><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/property-binding#colspan-and-colspan\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h4><h4 translation-origin=\"off\"><code>colspan</code> and <code>colSpan</code><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/property-binding#colspan-and-colspan\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h4>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">最容易混淆的地方是 <code>colspan</code> 這個 Attribute 和 <code>colSpan</code> 這個 Property。請注意，這兩個名稱只有一個字母的大小寫不同。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A common point of confusion is between the attribute, <code>colspan</code>, and the property, <code>colSpan</code>.  Notice that these two names differ by only a single letter.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要透過 <code>colSpan</code> 使用屬性繫結，請鍵入以下內容：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To use property binding using <code>colSpan</code>, type the following:</p>\n\n<code-example path=\"attribute-binding/src/app/app.component.html\" region=\"colSpan\" header=\"src/app/app.component.html\">\n&lt;!-- Notice the colSpan property is camel case --&gt;\n&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td [colSpan]=\"1 + 1\"&gt;Three-Four&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;\n\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要在元件的 <code>isUnchanged</code> 屬性為 <code>true</code> 時禁用按鈕，請鍵入以下內容：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To disable a button while the component's <code>isUnchanged</code> property is <code>true</code>, type the following:</p>\n\n<code-example path=\"property-binding/src/app/app.component.html\" region=\"disabled-button\" header=\"src/app/app.component.html\">\n&lt;!-- Bind button disabled state to `isUnchanged` property --&gt;\n&lt;button type=\"button\" [disabled]=\"isUnchanged\"&gt;Disabled Button&lt;/button&gt;\n\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要設定指令的屬性，請鍵入以下內容：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To set a property of a directive, type the following:</p>\n\n<code-example path=\"property-binding/src/app/app.component.html\" region=\"class-binding\" header=\"src/app/app.component.html\">\n&lt;p [<a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a>]=\"classes\"&gt;[<a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a>] binding to the classes property making this blue&lt;/p&gt;\n\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要將自訂元件的模型屬性設定為供父元件和子元件互相通訊的，請鍵入以下內容：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To set the model property of a custom component for parent and child components to communicate with each other, type the following:</p>\n\n<code-example path=\"property-binding/src/app/app.component.html\" region=\"model-property-binding\" header=\"src/app/app.component.html\">\n&lt;app-item-detail [childItem]=\"parentItem\"&gt;&lt;/app-item-detail&gt;\n\n</code-example>\n<h2 id=\"toggling-button-features\" translation-result=\"on\">切換按鈕功能<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/property-binding#toggling-button-features\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Toggling button features<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/property-binding#toggling-button-features\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<!-- vale Angular.Google_WordListSuggestions = NO -->\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要使用布林值來禁用某個按鈕的特性，請將 DOM 屬性 <code>disabled</code> 繫結到此類中的某個 Boolean 型屬性。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To use a Boolean value to disable a button's features, bind the <code>disabled</code> DOM attribute to a Boolean property in the class.</p>\n\n<!-- vale Angular.Google_WordListSuggestions = YES -->\n<code-example path=\"property-binding/src/app/app.component.html\" region=\"disabled-button\" header=\"src/app/app.component.html\">\n&lt;!-- Bind button disabled state to `isUnchanged` property --&gt;\n&lt;button type=\"button\" [disabled]=\"isUnchanged\"&gt;Disabled Button&lt;/button&gt;\n\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">由於 <code>AppComponent</code> 中屬性 <code>isUnchanged</code> 的值是 <code>true</code>，Angular 會禁用該按鈕。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Because the value of the property <code>isUnchanged</code> is <code>true</code> in the <code>AppComponent</code>, Angular disables the button.</p>\n\n<code-example path=\"property-binding/src/app/app.component.ts\" region=\"boolean\" header=\"src/app/app.component.ts\">\nisUnchanged = true;\n\n</code-example>\n<h2 id=\"whats-next\" translation-result=\"on\">下一步呢？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/property-binding#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">What's next<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/property-binding#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/property-binding-best-practices\">屬性繫結的最佳實踐</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/property-binding-best-practices\">Property binding best practices</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/event-binding\">事件繫結</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/event-binding\">Event binding</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/interpolation\">文字插值</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/interpolation\">Text Interpolation</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/class-binding\">類和樣式繫結</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/class-binding\">Class &amp; Style Binding</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/attribute-binding\">attribute 繫結</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/attribute-binding\">Attribute Binding</a></p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：4/14/2022</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/ajs-quick-reference\n - guide/architecture-components\n - guide/attribute-binding\n - guide/binding-overview\n - guide/built-in-directives\n - guide/class-binding\n - guide/event-binding\n - guide/example-apps-list\n - guide/glossary\n - guide/inputs-outputs\n - guide/interpolation\n - guide/router-reference\n - guide/template-overview\n - guide/template-syntax\n - guide/two-way-binding\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06\n - tutorial/tour-of-heroes/toh-pt3\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/NgClass\n - api/common/NgOptimizedImage\n - api/core/ContentChild\n - api/core/ViewChild\n - guide/architecture-components\n - guide/attribute-binding\n - guide/binding-syntax\n - guide/class-binding\n - guide/event-binding\n - guide/glossary#template\n - guide/interpolation\n - guide/property-binding#binding-to-a-property\n - guide/property-binding#colspan-and-colspan\n - guide/property-binding#colspan-和-colspan\n - guide/property-binding#prerequisites\n - guide/property-binding#property-binding\n - guide/property-binding#setting-an-element-property-to-a-component-property-value\n - guide/property-binding#toggling-button-features\n - guide/property-binding#understanding-the-flow-of-data\n - guide/property-binding#whats-next\n - guide/property-binding#下一步呢\n - guide/property-binding#瞭解資料流\n - guide/property-binding#切換按鈕功能\n - guide/property-binding#前提條件\n - guide/property-binding#將元素的屬性設定為元件屬性的值\n - guide/property-binding#屬性繫結\n - guide/property-binding#繫結到屬性\n - guide/property-binding-best-practices\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/property-binding.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n-->"}